org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT users.* FROM users INNER JOIN members ON members.user_id = users.id WHERE users.status = "$1" AND members.project_id = 1 AND users.status = "$2" AND users.type IN ("$3", "$4") LIMIT "$5"
